nodes.text: "Crossing the Line" (German title "Grenzüberschreitung") is a comic strip written by Alec Worley, drawn by Ingo Römling and edited by Gunther Nickel. The story was published in the 4th issue of the German Star Wars Rebels Animation-Magazine, which was released on October 10, 2018. It was first published in English in the December 2019 issue of the Australian magazine K-Zone.
